data.title: Meet Our Fremont Dentists
data.meta_description: Our Fremont & San Lorenzo dentists are all committed to providing you with the best dental experience catered to your needs! Visit our site to learn more!
data.text:
Dr. Paul Nguyen

After majoring in psychology at UC Davis, Dr. Paul Nguyen graduated from the University of the Pacific School of Dentistry in 1996. Dr. Nguyen keeps up with the latest technology and techniques in dentistry with active memberships in the American Dental Association, California Dental Association, Southern Alameda Dental Society, and the International Congress of Oral Implantologists.

Dr. Nguyen met his wife, Katlyn, in dental school and now they share this practice together. When he's away from the office, Dr. Nguyen enjoys traveling, reading, music and sports. He is involved in various community services to help the underprivileged.

Dr. Katlyn Nguyen

After majoring in biological science at UC Davis, Dr. Katlyn Nguyen graduated from the prestigious University of the Pacific Dental School in 1995. She finds her job very pleasing, rewarding, especially when she transforms a dental phobic patient into a normal, calmly, blissful patient who is no longer afraid of dentist.

Dr. Nguyen stays updated on the advances in her field as a member of many professional organizations, including the American Dental Association, California Dental Association and the Southern Alameda Dental Society and the International Congress of Oral Implantologists. Dr. Nguyen enjoys traveling, exercise, reading, camping and spending time with her son and daughter.

Dr. Nolan Dang

Dr. Nolan graduated from UC Davis with a degree in Genetics and Genomics and then went on to UCLA School of Dentistry where he received his DDS in 2023. Dr. Nolan is passionate about providing excellent dental care for all of his patients. He aims to make all of his patients feel welcomed and comfortable for every appointment. In his free time, Dr. Nolan enjoys traveling, watching sports, and exploring the outdoors.
